module.simplesync.model

Class SyncJob

  • java.lang.Object
    • module.simplesync.model.SyncJob
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<java.util.concurrent.Delayed>, java.util.concurrent.Delayed

    public final class SyncJob
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.util.concurrent.Delayed
    Object to store data of a synchronization job. Especially it stores the date when a requeued/postponed job may be retried.
    Author:
    Stefan Werner
